yright markers using specialized software, and then =E2=80=9Cseeded=E2=80=
=9D the books to other users worldwide. Even more damningly, Boies=E2=80=99=
 team says they have <em>proof</em> that Zuckerberg personally approved the=
 use of a pirated dataset, despite internal concerns. This is where things =
